for Fall, 2007. Here you may find lists of <a href="hw.html">homework assignments</a>, 
dates for <a href="quiz.html">quizzes</a>, as well as lists of topics covered by these quizzes,
an html-ized copy of the <a href="203fd.html">course summary</a>, and anything else that
might come up. Click <a href="inclass/">HERE</a> to find various items presented in class.</center>


